<Layout title="Comparing Competing Offers With Different Conditions: A Brisbane Sellers Framework 2026 | Daniel Gierach Property" description="When competing offers on your Brisbane property arrive with different prices, deposits, conditions and settlement dates, the highest number rarely wins on a risk-adjusted basis. Here is the framework for converting apples-to-oranges offers into a like-for-like comparison." schema={faqSchema}>

<article style="background:var(--color-surface-0);min-height:100vh;">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div style="background:#0a0806;padding:8rem 0 3rem;">
    <div class="max-w-[780px] mx-auto px-8">
